{"tid":1261283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不合作運動do and don't(新手入門指南)","createTime":"2019-06-27T07:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T13:24:11.000Z","uid":267654,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"770a31720df986195c0d09710a44b120680b1eb6","tid":1261283,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"我發夢見到有一份咁既指南，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該各位新手望望先好去不合作運動，唔係就做幾多次道歉團都會失民心</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />指南仲有例子舉埋<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">，唔好再亂同市民嘈，一路不合作一路民意加分。</span></span>份野我發夢時睇過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">甘地</span></span>佢地點做架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/V6j9qxY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FV6j9qxY.jpg&h=6b89cb27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DJ2jAux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDJ2jAux.jpg&h=bb5066e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文字版：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【不合作運動參與者指南與實戰】 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n≪指南篇≫<br />\n<br />\n1.\t原因（why）︰透過不合作運動，對政府造成滋擾及壓力，以迫使政府回應民間訴求<br />\n<br />\n2.\t行動內容（what）︰以游擊的群眾聚集，進行滋擾<br />\n<br />\n2.1\t阻礙政府部工作，如警總、稅局、入境、海關、立法會、政總等<br />\n<br />\n2.2\t癱瘓公共事業／交通，如巴士、港鐵、水電公司等<br />\n<br />\n3.\t態度（how）︰對於阻礙及滋擾，群眾可以用誠意、謙卑的態度表達抱歉，但需堅持不合作的精神及對準政權出擊<br />\n<br />\n4.\t不合作底線︰不影響醫療、法院運作為大前題；而進退方向，由現場群眾決定，請留意網絡消息及溝通<br />\n<br />\n5.\t避免︰與上班／路過的市民爭執或肢體衝突 (避免失民心及被拍黑材料)。若對方撞過來，先舉高雙手，以示沒有動作，但受到攻擊時，請務必以恰當方式保護自己<br />\n<br />\n≪實戰篇≫ (舉例說明)<br />\n<br />\n6.你做咩係度阻住我返工？你有你表達意見，我有權利返工。<br />\n<br />\n*表示明白對方需要，say sorry<br />\n*講已有200萬人上街政府都無理會<br />\n*利用非暴力手段影響政府運作來抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. 你地正暴徒，有咩不滿就圍人掟雞蛋。<br />\n<br />\n*扔雞蛋都令你感暴力，堅say sorry<br />\n*雞蛋是對強權的表達並沒殺傷力<br />\n*即使警方於6.12暴力對待示威者，我地只會選擇不合作運動<br />\n*不合作運動原則是非暴力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8. 都講左暫緩你地仲唔收手，係咪另有目的呀？/係咪收錢做野呀？<br />\n<br />\n*暫緩不等如撤回。咁都唔肯改字眼，林鄭另有所謀？<br />\n*難以想像有邊間機構會動用數億去叫200百萬人上街？<br />\n*堅決不撤不散不要代住先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位幫手推推分享 ，6.24日稅務的不合作運動太多新手，如果跟住的日子再道多幾次歉就會輸</span></span>。"},{"pid":"51331e54c8c97d112dc505584832023bd2c57f89","tid":1261283,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"say sorry活動真係世界一級<br />\n係咪開先河?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f65853c019b1ab007e612a4bb2538f42369d000","tid":1261283,"uid":263555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e623d7187883c4d4d6ebba20575a6a6e859c6b6","tid":1261283,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26db473eba16c717814a3eeb8519dd8007d190a9","tid":1261283,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51331e54c8c97d112dc505584832023bd2c57f89","tid":1261283,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"say sorry活動真係世界一級<br />\n係咪開先河?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"有人話係風土病呀！"},{"pid":"244e2777c1cff03bb93a1ab9d9a73b25d3489f41","tid":1261283,"uid":110895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26db473eba16c717814a3eeb8519dd8007d190a9","tid":1261283,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc